1 (7) If the award from the fund exceeds one million dollars, the documentation required
2 to demonstrate proof of payment for all expenditures for which the applicant seeks
3 reimbursement;
4 (8) The process by which an award is disbursed; and
5 (9) The process by which any moneys awarded from the fund are returned to the fund
6 in the event of a change in the project's circumstances, the applicant's failure to
7 meet the established performance expectations, or the projects failure or relocation
8 outside of the state.
